  'An 8-hour private car charter for Busan cruise passengers with a licensed English-speaking driver-guide. Default itinerary covers UN Memorial Cemetery, Taejongdae cliffs, Gamcheon Culture Village, Yongdusan Park, and Jagalchi Market. Fully customizable. Pickup at the cruise terminal, KTX station, or any central Busan hotel; on-time return to the ship is guaranteed.',
